        What to Expect When Selling in Greenslopes
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Greenslopes sits on the ridge between Coorparoo and Holland Park, with strong family appeal and a buyer pool that responds well to character and presentation.
      </p>
